description: Aker Carbon Capture ASA operates as a carbon capture company. The company operates a carbon capture plant; and engages in the downstream processing and management of CO2. It also offers aftermarket support services to industrial plant owners and operators across various industries to reduce and remove CO2 emissions. The company operates carbon capture plants under the Just Catch, Big Catch, Just Catch Offshore, and Mobile Test Unit brands. It operates in Norway, Denmark, Sweden, the United Kingdom, the Netherlands, India, and the United States. Aker Carbon Capture ASA was incorporated in 2020 and is headquartered in Lysaker, Norway.
